SUMMARY:Blind Date with a Book
LOCATION:W Kennedy Blvd &amp\; W Grand Central Ave Tampa \, FL 33602 Unite
 d States
DESCRIPTION:Its a match! Swipe right on a good read and start a new chapte
 r together during Blind Date with a Book. Each novel has page-turner poten
 tial but is wrapped to hide the cover  its bound to be good! Join us to un
 wrap a new favorite and experience love at first page. This event happens 
 four times a year\, so its the perfect opportunity to stay booked and busy
 ! WHEN: February 9\, May 11\, August 10\, November 9  4:30-7:30pm WHERE: S
 now Park We are partnering with Oxford Exchange and TeBella Tea Company on
  this program. In addition\, huge thank you to our sponsordonor the Hillsb
 orough Public Library (Seminole Heights Location) for their help with this
  program. El amor est en el aire! Comienza tu nueva historia de amor con n
 uestra Cita a Ciegas Con Un Libro. Cada obra viene envuelta y ocultando su
  portada. La idea es que el libro que escojas sea una sorpresa! Acompanos 
 para descubrir tu nueva aventura (y quin sabe? tal vez un amor a primera p
 gina). El evento es cuatro veces al ao\, as que es la oportunidad perfecta
  para mantenerte ocupado! CUANDO: 9 de febrero\, 11 de mayo\, 10 de agosto
 \, 9 de noviembre  4:30-7:30pm DONDE: Parque Snow \n\nPermalink: https://w
