SUMMARY:Studio55: Encaustic Explorations
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa FL 33602 Tampa \, FL 33602 United St
 ates
DESCRIPTION:Explore the world of Encaustic art\, an ancient form of painti
 ng with hot pigmented beeswax used in a modern way! During this course par
 ticipants will learn about encaustic history\, materials\, and safety. In 
 this 4-day intensive workshop\, students will explore a variety of techniq
 ues such as incising\, layering\, pigment sticks\, mark-making\, mixed med
 ia collage and monotypes. Designed for beginners and advanced skills alike
 \, we will work together to focus on taking your encaustic journey to a ne
 w level! Monday  Thursday\, Jun 29  Jul 2  10:00 AM  4:00 PM (4 classes) A
 ges 55  Beginner Level All supplies Included \n\nPermalink: https://www.ta
 mpa.gov/node/188726
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/188726
END:VEVENT
