 endrickson will facilitate meetings of the 2025 Charter Review Advisory Co
 mmission. The commissions purpose is to review the Tampa Home Rule Charter
  of 1975\, as amended\, and propose any amendments or revisions by majorit
 y vote of the Commission\, and present a report with their recommendations
  to City Council\, which may by two-thirds vote of City Council be placed 
